author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Kitchen backsplash metal profile tips…I’m using chrome Schluter JOLLY. I cut it using a Diablo 84 tooth non-ferrous blade for aluminum. The CaliBro square is invaluable because it stabilizes the profile and helps prevent kickback. I embed the JOLLY in thin-set mortar and immediately start setting tile. Visit me at homerepairtutor.com for more tips 🔥#kitchenbacksplash #homerenovation #tilebacksplash #homerepairtutor
